            "CampaignProgressInfo": "A malfunction in the Atlas launch vehicle caused by an anomaly resulted in an abort, and the loss of the launch vehicle. This has caused a bit of a setback, but we are on track again. Since then, Astronaut Patrick successfully followed with an identical mission to yours, currently holding the record of longest time in space."
        }
