    "CompletionMessage": "After the success and completion of the final Mercury mission where you orbited 24 times, it was concluded that all resources would be moved into the development of the next space program, and the journey towards the Moon. Project Mercury met its objectives, and some of the Mercury astronauts will continue their careers in Project Gemini."
